title: DayTwoCherry
---
//Cherry
Ah. Good morning (name)

//MC
-> Good morning Cherry!
    <<set $friendship +=1>>
-> Hello
-> (say nothing)
    <<set $friendship -=1>>
    
//MC
So, how are you?

//Cherry
<<if $friendship >=4>>
Honestly? I've been better. I won't lie, this isn't the most comfortable cell I've seen, these clothes are starting to itch a bit, and I've started talking to the walls for company. So, could be a bit better, I guess!
<<jump improvement>>
<<endif>>
<<if $friendship <=4>>
I'm doing perfectly well, thank you very much. What a lovely place for me to be staying in.
<<jump improvement>>
<<endif>>
