title: improvement
---
//MC
Well maybe we can help each other out? Is there something I can do to improve your... living area?

//Cherry
Well depends. What would you want in return?

//MC
Just information. I want to know more about you, and how you ended up, the way you are.

//Cherry
Well in that case... A (TASK) here would be nice. If you like.

//MC
-> Accept
    <<set $friendship +=1>>
    I'm sure I can figure something like that out for you.
    //Cherry
    Thankyou, it is much appreciated. If I think of something worth sharing, you'll be the first I tell.
-> Decline
    <<set $friendship -=1>>
    //Cherry
    Well. I see how it is then.

<<if $friendship >=6>>
//Cherry
So... I've kind of heard others talking about what this place is. But like... what (do) you do?
//MC
I'm security?
//Cherry
No silly, as in this place?
//MC
Oh! The Orion Institute is designed to study entities, such as yourself.
//Cherry
Yeah, but why?
//MC
Uh. I don't, actually know. Huh.
<<endif>>

//Cherry
So, who runs this place? Who will, eventually, have the pleasure of interrogating me, hm?

//MC
-> (truth)
    <<set $friendship +=1>>
    His name is Magnus Owens, our institutes director. He's quite chill, don't worry, although he can be scary when he's mad.
-> (avoid)
    Who, Magnus? He's no one, don't even worry about it.
-> (lie)
    HA, Magnus will eat you alive
    <<set $friendship -=1>>

//Cherry
Magnus... now why does that name ring a bell?

//MC
Maybe someone else has told you about him? He's quite a popular boss.

//Cherry
Hm. Maybe.

...

//MC
Can I ask you something?

//Cherry
Shoot.

-> Name
    <<jump name>>
-> Arrival
    <<jump arrival>>
-> Nevermind
    <<jump goodbye>>
